It takes a bit of time to wrangle with the particular CSS Toolkit that you use - but once youâ€™ve got it up and running it is usually fairly straightforward to customize.

In theGames/index.html update the sidebar to include the Bootstrap specific classes when presenting categories:

{% block sidebar %}


<UL class="nav nav-list">
        <LI class="nav-header">Event List</LI>
        {% if event_list %}
                {% for event in event_list %}
                       <LI>{{ event.name }}</A></LI>
                {% endfor %}
        {% else %}
                <LI>No Event at present.</LI>
        {% endif %}
</UL>

{% endblock %}


